name: Rosh Hashanah
notes: The Jewish New Year begins at sundown on Monday, 22 September 2025 and ends at nightfall on Wednesday, 24 September 2025【660010001723347†L17-L19】【760097705158339†L30-L32】.

name: Yom Kippur
notes: Yom Kippur (Day of Atonement) for 2025 starts on Wednesday, 1 October 2025 at sunset and ends on Thursday, 2 October 2025 at nightfall【760097705158339†L40-L43】.

name: Sukkot
notes: Sukkot in 2025 begins on Monday, 6 October at sunset and continues until Monday, 13 October at nightfall【760097705158339†L50-L53】.

name: Shemini Atzeret
notes: Shemini Atzeret in the Diaspora begins at sunset on Monday, 13 October 2025 and ends at nightfall on Tuesday, 14 October【760097705158339†L61-L63】.

name: Simchat Torah
notes: Simchat Torah in the Diaspora begins at sunset on Tuesday, 14 October 2025 and ends at nightfall on Wednesday, 15 October【760097705158339†L61-L67】.
